<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Supprimer le Quartier</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Supprimer le quartier</h1>
        
        <div class="alert alert-danger">
            <h4>Êtes-vous sûr de vouloir supprimer ce quartier ?</h4>
            <p><strong>Nom:</strong> <%= quartier.nom %></p>
            <p><strong>Poids:</strong> <%= quartier.poids %></p>
        </div>
        
        <form action="/quartiers/delete/<%= quartier._id %>" method="POST">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Confirmer la suppression</button>
            <a href="/quartiers" class="btn btn-secondary">Annuler</a>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>